    {
      "id": "PopularPost70586",
      "post_content": "I do like that it provides good card advantage, which isn't common in red. You get to make your opponent [Terminate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terminate) his own creature, etc. But it does cost a lot to cast for a response spell, and you can't very well be leaving four mana open every turn waiting for your opponent to do something. As a sideboard against blue, though, it's a no-brainer.  \nOne question: Can you use this on [Cruel Ultimatum](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Ultimatum) in a regular two-player game? The card says \"target opponent\" rather than \"target player\", so if your opponent casts it, you can't make him target himself instead, right?",
      "posted_by": "achilleselbow",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost70586\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I do like that it provides good card advantage, which isn't common in red. You get to make your opponent <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terminate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terminate\">Terminate</a> his own creature, etc. But it does cost a lot to cast for a response spell, and you can't very well be leaving four mana open every turn waiting for your opponent to do something. As a sideboard against blue, though, it's a no-brainer.<br/>One question: Can you use this on <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cruel Ultimatum\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Ultimatum\">Cruel Ultimatum</a> in a regular two-player game? The card says \"target opponent\" rather than \"target player\", so if your opponent casts it, you can't make him target himself instead, right?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '70586'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy31177\">achilleselbow</span>\r\n                                (5/2/2010 8:22:14 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                    