    {
      "id": "PopularPost133770",
      "post_content": "My first thought was that I wish they'd just reprint [Red Elemental Blast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Red Elemental Blast) or [Pyroblast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroblast).  \n  \nHowever, this has the ability to counter or redirect a lot of other things. Basically, this is a red [Deflection](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Deflection) with the added benefit of only costing R if the opponent cast a blue spell.  \n  \nText could almost read: R - Counter target Counter, but it does a lot more than that.   \n  \nToo bad so many spells like [Jace's Ingenuit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace's Ingenuit)y, [Foresee](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Foresee), and [Preordain](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Preordain) are caster only rather than target player. Would love to catch a [Blue Sun's Zenith](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blue Sun's Zenith) with this but definitely limited in Standar.  \n  \nNot sure about [Cruel Ultimatum](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Ultimatum) since from your perspective the caster is a target opponent. I think it could work.",
      "posted_by": "Nighthawk42",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost133770\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">My first thought was that I wish they'd just reprint <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Red Elemental Blast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Red Elemental Blast\">Red Elemental Blast</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pyroblast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroblast\">Pyroblast</a>.<br/><br/>However, this has the ability to counter or redirect a lot of other things.  Basically, this is a red <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Deflection\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Deflection\">Deflection</a> with the added benefit of only costing R if the opponent cast a blue spell.<br/><br/>Text could almost read:  R - Counter target Counter, but it does a lot more than that.  <br/><br/>Too bad so many spells like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jace's Ingenuit\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace's Ingenuit\">Jace's Ingenuit</a>y, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Foresee\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Foresee\">Foresee</a>, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Preordain\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Preordain\">Preordain</a> are caster only rather than target player.  Would love to catch a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blue Sun's Zenith\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blue Sun's Zenith\">Blue Sun's Zenith</a> with this but definitely limited in Standar.<br/><br/>Not sure about <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cruel Ultimatum\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Ultimatum\">Cruel Ultimatum</a> since from your perspective the caster is a target opponent.   I think it could work.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '133770'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy6213\">Nighthawk42</span>\r\n                                (2/17/2011 9:49:04 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
